---
import SharedPageLayout from "../components/SharedPageLayout.astro";
---

<SharedPageLayout title="Legal &amp; Compliance | Done Deal Digital" bodyClass="bg-background-light font-dmsans text-navy">
    <Fragment slot="head">
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&amp;family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=Work+Sans:wght@400;700&amp;family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#FF7B00",
                        "navy": "#0B1D33",
                        "concrete": "#E2E8F0",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#0B1D33",
                        "grid-gray": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)"
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Work Sans", "sans-serif"],
                        "bebas": ["Bebas Neue", "cursive"],
                        "dmsans": ["DM Sans", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        "none": "0",
                        "DEFAULT": "0",
                        "lg": "0",
                        "xl": "0",
                        "full": "9999px"
                    }
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @tailwind base;
        @tailwind components;
        @tailwind utilities;

        @layer utilities {
            .graph-paper {
                background-size: 40px 40px;
                background-image: 
                    linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                    linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            }
            .block-shadow {
                box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px rgba(11, 29, 51, 1);
            }
            .bebas-heavy {
                font-weight: 700;
                letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            }
        }
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
    </style>
</Fragment>

<section class="relative bg-navy py-16 border-b-2 border-navy overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 graph-paper opacity-30"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
<div class="inline-block border-2 border-primary px-4 py-1 mb-4">
<span class="text-white font-bebas text-lg tracking-[.2em]">LEGAL &amp; COMPLIANCE</span>
</div>
<h1 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white uppercase leading-none">
            Transparent terms for a <span class="text-primary">straight-talk</span> business.
        </h1>
<p class="text-concrete/60 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mt-4">Last Updated: October 24, 2024</p>
</div>
</section>
<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid lg:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12">
<aside class="hidden lg:block">
<div class="sticky top-32 border-2 border-navy p-6 bg-white">
<h3 class="font-bebas text-2xl text-navy mb-6 border-b-2 border-navy pb-2">DOCUMENT SECTIONS</h3>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li><a class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2" href="#privacy"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-navy"></span> Privacy Policy</a></li>
<li><a class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2" href="#tos"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-navy"></span> Terms of Service</a></li>
<li><a class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2" href="#cookies"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-navy"></span> Cookie Policy</a></li>
<li><a class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2" href="#data-requests"><span class="w-2 h-2 bg-navy"></span> Data Requests</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</aside>
<article class="bg-white border border-gray-300 p-8 md:p-16">
<section class="mb-20" id="privacy">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-5xl text-navy mb-8">1. PRIVACY POLICY</h2>
<div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
<p>This Privacy Policy describes how Done Deal Digital ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you visit or make a purchase from our site. We focus on the trades—plumbers, roofers, and HVAC pros—and we treat your data with the same respect we give to a job site.</p>
<h3 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy mt-10">INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h3>
<p>When you visit the site, we automatically collect certain information about your device, including information about your web browser, IP address, time zone, and some of the cookies that are installed on your device.</p>
<div class="bg-background-light border-l-4 border-primary p-6 my-8">
<p class="font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-navy mb-4">DATA COLLECTION CATEGORIES:</p>
<ul class="space-y-3">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-1 material-symbols-outlined text-sm">square</span> <span><strong>Contact Info:</strong> Name, business name, email, and phone number for project inquiries.</span></li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-1 material-symbols-outlined text-sm">square</span> <span><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Browser type, operating system, and IP address for site security.</span></li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-1 material-symbols-outlined text-sm">square</span> <span><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you navigate our blueprints and service pages.</span></li>
</ul>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy mt-10">THIRD-PARTY PROCESSORS</h3>
<p>We share your Personal Information with third parties to help us use your Personal Information, as described above. We only work with industry-standard partners:</p>
<ul class="list-none space-y-4">
<li class="border-2 border-navy/5 p-4 flex justify-between items-center">
<span class="font-bold">Google Analytics</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold bg-navy text-white px-2 py-1 uppercase">Analytics</span>
</li>
<li class="border-2 border-navy/5 p-4 flex justify-between items-center">
<span class="font-bold">Meta Pixel</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold bg-navy text-white px-2 py-1 uppercase">Marketing</span>
</li>
<li class="border-2 border-navy/5 p-4 flex justify-between items-center">
<span class="font-bold">Mailchimp</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold bg-navy text-white px-2 py-1 uppercase">Communications</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<section class="mb-20 pt-20 border-t-2 border-navy/10" id="tos">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-5xl text-navy mb-8">2. TERMS OF SERVICE</h2>
<div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
<p>By accessing this website, you are agreeing to be bound by these website Terms and Conditions of Use, all applicable laws and regulations, and agree that you are responsible for compliance with any applicable local laws.</p>
<h3 class="font-bebas text-3xl text-navy mt-10">SERVICE AGREEMENTS</h3>
<p>Our digital marketing services are specifically designed for trade professionals. All project timelines and deliverables are outlined in individual project blueprints provided during the consultation phase.</p>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-6">
<h4 class="font-bold uppercase mb-2">User License</h4>
<p class="text-sm">Permission is granted to temporarily download one copy of the materials (information or software) on Done Deal Digital's website for personal, non-commercial transitory viewing only.</p>
</div>
<div class="border-2 border-navy p-6 bg-navy text-white">
<h4 class="font-bold uppercase mb-2 text-primary">Limitations</h4>
<p class="text-sm">In no event shall Done Deal Digital or its suppliers be liable for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for loss of data or profit) arising out of the use or inability to use the materials.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="mb-20 pt-20 border-t-2 border-navy/10" id="cookies">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-5xl text-navy mb-8">3. COOKIE POLICY</h2>
<div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
<p>Cookies are small pieces of text sent by your web browser by a website you visit. A cookie file is stored in your web browser and allows the Service or a third-party to recognize you and make your next visit easier and more useful to you.</p>
<p>We use cookies to understand site usage and to improve the content and offerings on our sites. For example, we may use cookies to personalize your experience at our web pages (e.g., to recognize you by name when you return to our site).</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="pt-20 border-t-2 border-navy/10" id="data-requests">
<div class="bg-navy p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
<h2 class="font-bebas bebas-heavy text-4xl text-primary mb-6">DATA &amp; ACCESS REQUESTS</h2>
<p class="mb-8 text-concrete/80 leading-relaxed">You have the right to access personal information we hold about you and to ask that your personal information be corrected, updated, or deleted. If you would like to exercise this right, please contact us through the information below.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/10 p-4 border border-white/20 w-full md:w-auto">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">mail</span>
<span class="font-bold">legal@donedealdigital.com</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/10 p-4 border border-white/20 w-full md:w-auto">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-bold uppercase text-sm">123 Industrial Way, Suite 400</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</article>
</main>

</SharedPageLayout>
